## English

### ğŸ“– Overview
A simple question bank application developed with Godot, supporting online verification and compatible with both desktop and Android platforms.

### âœ¨ Features
- ğŸ“ Basic question input and management
- ğŸ¯ Random question answering
- ğŸ” Check all questions or specific questions
- ğŸ–¼ï¸ Support for questions with images (single image)
- ğŸ“Š Rain Classroom question bank import
- ğŸ“± Cross-platform support (Windows & Android)
- â˜ï¸ Online verification system
- â±ï¸ Real-time timer and progress tracking
- ğŸ“ˆ Accuracy rate statistics
- ğŸ¨ Customizable backgrounds
- âŒ Mistake notebook functionality
- ğŸ” Simple login interface
- ğŸ“¤ Export functionality

### ğŸ“¥ Download
- **Android**: Download APK from [Releases]()
- **Windows**: Download executable from [Releases]()

### ğŸš€ Changelog

#### V2.01.6.57 (2025/11/22)
- Optimized login logic
- Username persistence (no need to re-enter every time)

#### V2.01.6.5 (2025/11/15)
- Major code refactoring
- Restructured node architecture
- Android can now connect to verification server (no local verification required)

#### V2.01.6.4 (2025/10/19)
- Added compatibility for image-based multiple choice questions
- Implemented a simple login interface

#### V2.01.6.2 (2025/10/11)
- Added compatibility for short answer questions

#### V2.01.6 (2025/10/03)
- Added mistake notebook feature
- Incorrect questions are saved to `mistake_note` folder in root directory

#### V2.01.5 (2025/09/24)
- Added background input system

#### V2.01.3 (2025/09/04)
- Export version completed
- Initial APK release

#### V2.0 (2025/08/30)
- Source code refactoring
- Compatibility for non-image question banks and B-type multiple choice questions
- Updated random answering feature

### ğŸ› Known Issues
- Inserting images may cause interface layout issues
- Some compatibility issues with specific question formats

### ğŸ”§ Technical Details
- **Engine**: Godot Engine
- **Language**: GDScript
- **Platforms**: Windows, Android
- **Network**: Online verification support

